      "comment": "FREE SETTLER (7) was strongly fancied last time on the back of some good form but disappointed when fourth (20.10) at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Has claims if he runs up to expectations. HARA'S CHIEF (2) missed the frame but ran a slick fourth at this track over 366m in 19.86. Harder here but expected to measure up. UNACCEPTABLE ROB (1) goes very well this course and distance starting 11 times for four wins and two minors. Was out of the placings last time (19.19) at Q Straight in a Grade 5, finishing fourth and beaten 1.5 lengths. Among the main chances. I'M THE PROBLEM (8) has ability and can find the frame.",
